content: imholders: Focused on documentation management with 8 merged PRs this month, including significant changes to README files in multiple languages. Notable contributions include adding README_MY.md in PR #4567 (+58010/-24580 lines), adding translation files in PR #4704, and making several targeted updates to existing documentation. Activity was occasional throughout the month, with contributions on 7 different days primarily focused on documentation files (82% of changes).
